thnographic research and policy analysis, the authors analyze the cultural transition, tensions, and trajectory of this call toward active citizenship.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aAnttonen, Anneli, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBarnes, Marian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHäikiö, Liisa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKuhlmann, Ellen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeonardis, Ota de, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeveu, Catherine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNewman, Janet, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNewman, Janet, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTonkens, Evelien, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTonkens, Evelien, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aVabø, Mia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package Backfile 2000-2013z978311070067108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014z978311060651508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311102378608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2015z97831106627880 cprintz978908964275240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048513437?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048513437423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048513437/original  a978-3-11-060651-5  AUP eBook Package Backlist 2